audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "竜化したおれと互角に戦ったきみこそものすごい強さじゃないか。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110050_story/VO_CHR_110050_STORY_0033.wav", "vo_chr_110050_story/VO_CHR_110050_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "そういう意味ではない。オレが言いたいのは……まぁ、いいさ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110050_01.png", "speakerName": "ベルザーク", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110050_story/VO_CHR_110050_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "オレのような戦闘狂に、ここまで付き合ってくれたのは、お前が初めてだ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110050_01.png", "speakerName": "ベルザーク", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110050_story/VO_CHR_110050_STORY_0046.wav"], "content": "感謝するよ。ユーディル。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110050_01.png", "speakerName": "ベルザーク", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110050014, "title": "生の実感"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "くっ……敵の数が多すぎる……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "みんな、深追いはするな！魔獣を追い払いつつ、城まで撤退――", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "――ユーディル。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110050_01.png", "speakerName": "ベルザーク", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "みんなの心配ばかりしていないで、自分のことも気にかけろ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110050_01.png", "speakerName": "ベルザーク", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0007.wav", "vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0045.wav"], "content": "え……こんな近くに魔獣が……!?助かったよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"},